---
title: Keto Chicken Parmigiana with Buttery Green Beans
description: The 'chicken parm' has been a culinary classic of Italian-American and Australian restaurants since the '50s. With good reason: It’s divine! We’ve removed the breadcrumbs to make it suitable for keto, but it’s still got a golden cheese crust.
